                    <b>Challenges:</b> The biggest challenges was vertical alignment, with responsive design in mind. Two areas I had trouble with were
                    making sure that the fixed navbar wasn't covering text and the footer stuck to the bottom (it kept floating up on mobile devices).
                </li>
