                    with a calulated height, which was fixed by adding a min-height to the container so the text doesn't break ' .
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <b>What I learned:</b> I learned that designing a website from scratch can be difficult,
                    not in terms of code but in terms of choosing colors, designing layouts, figuring out what look you want to acheive, etc.
                    I learned bootstrap, using the grid system, flexbox, aligning text, navbars, and more. I also learned how to create and apply custom css.
                </li>
